      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for purchase is a mechanically sound E92 BMW M3, featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 engine. This high-revving powerplant delivers 414 hp through eight individual throttle bodies and is mated to a driver-centric 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis remains taut, utilizing the M Variable Differential Lock for superior lateral grip and corner-exit traction. Recent preventative maintenance includes the critical rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators, ensuring the valvetrain and reciprocating assembly are in peak operating condition. While the aesthetics show minor patina consistent with a well-loved driver's car, the mechanical synchronization and atmospheric induction note remain flawless. A purist-spec example ready for the B-roads.",
